              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-200 slide-from-right"><svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><circle cx="10" cy="10" r="10" fill="#a78bfa"/><path d="M7 10l3 3 3-3" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>Workflows that save hours each week</li>
